Effective Date: 2026
T I Rides ("we", "our", or "the app") is operated by Tony's Team. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, protect, and handle your information when you use our taxi and ride service application.
By using T I Rides, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
